r employer=E2=80=99s stock just before a major announcement, or =E2=80=9Cno=
pe, never heard of any of these people,=E2=80=9D which will look really bad=
 if your colleague overhears and is like =E2=80=9Cwell but this is your gir=
lfriend=E2=80=99s name=E2=80=9D and you are like =E2=80=9Cwhat?=E2=80=9D an=
d he is like =E2=80=9Cand her address is the same as yours=E2=80=9D and you=
