ys together last week=E2=80=9D and you are like "what?=E2=80=9D and he is l=
ike =E2=80=9Cyou were buying a boat.=E2=80=9D[13]</p><p style=3D"margin: 16=
px 0;">I do not give legal advice around here but I will say that if you ti=
p your live-in romantic partner with secret inside information about your e=
